{"tid":1503892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(技巧)長槍突點就係長 請向前刺擊","createTime":"2019-08-25T06:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T12:07:25.000Z","uid":78222,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6a19b20443a993b89073b2e0751cfabfcec2fc44","tid":1503892,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住！<br />\n長撚最好係向前刺擊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">長</span></span></strong>撚優勢係可以<span style=\"color: orange;\">拉開距離</span>攻擊 <br />\n唔洗完全埋身<br />\n 請<span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手捉實向前刺</span>(有盾就單手)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8UybEdUDdxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8UybEdUDdxM&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=88e89c20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8UybEdUDdxM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WoGEiEq-wFo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWoGEiEq-wFo&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=98665f83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WoGEiEq-wFo</a><br />\n<br />\n由上下而扑個啲係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>短撚</strong></span>先用 <br />\n而短撚啲傷係靠上而下揮個下力扑<br />\n你長撚仲想扑隻手會好累<br />\n<br />\n無論mhw長槍同劍擊都係<span style=\"color: orange;\">向前刺擊</span><br />\n咁就會用到最大效用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"0e9bfe27bf763464dba544a17619fdbc9200f04e","tid":1503892,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"記住mhw嘅長槍統槍<br />\n都係十下刺先一兩下扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ead930f37cedef9d25789aa76665130a8f7cf26","tid":1503892,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"向劍撃運